<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 03:12:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国电动汽车初创公司蔚来为新版ET7轿车设定起价</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-startup-nio-sets-starting-price-new-version-et7-sedan-2024-04-25/</link><description>中国电动汽车 (EV) 初创公司 Nio 首席执行官周四表示，已将新版 ET7 轿车的起价定为 428,000 元人民币（59,063 美元）。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 02:56:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-startup-nio-sets-starting-price-new-version-et7-sedan-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>比亚迪推出阳王品牌第三款超豪华车型</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-unveils-third-ultra-luxury-model-under-yangwang-brand-2024-04-25/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪周四推出了阳王品牌的第三款超豪华车型U7，在价格战愈演愈烈的情况下，该公司进军高端市场以提高盈利能力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 02:48:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-unveils-third-ultra-luxury-model-under-yangwang-brand-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>台湾候任总统任命新团队称岛内安全困难</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-president-elect-appoints-new-team-says-islands-security-difficult-2024-04-25/</link><description>当选总统赖清德周四表示，台湾面临着困难的国家安全局势，而中国一直在逼近，他已在下个月上任前宣布了新的安全和外交团队的任命。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 02:45:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-president-elect-appoints-new-team-says-islands-security-difficult-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>日产推出四款概念车助推中国复兴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-unveils-four-concept-cars-fuel-china-comeback-2024-04-25/</link><description>日产汽车周四向中国市场推出了四款概念车，这家日本汽车制造商希望在全球最大的汽车市场收复失地。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 02:37:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-unveils-four-concept-cars-fuel-china-comeback-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>股市受科技股暴跌打击；日元在干预区震荡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-25/</link><description>亚洲股市周四下跌，Facebook 母公司 Meta Platforms 令人失望的盈利预测重创科技股，而日元兑美元自 1990 年以来首次跌破 155 美元，引发了东京干预的担忧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 02:32:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>小米SU7汽车订单锁定超7.5万辆 6月交付目标超万辆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-locks-over-75000-orders-su7-car-targets-over-10000-deliveries-june-2024-04-25/</link><description>中国智能手机制造商小米创始人雷军周四表示，截至 4 月 24 日，其运动型 SU7 电动轿车已锁定 75,723 辆订单，并计划在 6 月份交付超过 10,000 辆。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 02:19:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-locks-over-75000-orders-su7-car-targets-over-10000-deliveries-june-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>梅赛德斯表示将继续投资中国合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-benz-shows-off-electric-line-up-beijing-autoshow-not-giving-up-2024-04-25/</link><description>梅赛德斯奔驰中国区总裁周四表示，该公司将继续投资与互联网公司百度等中国合作伙伴的合作，并指出中国对其全球战略至关重要。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 02:02:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-benz-shows-off-electric-line-up-beijing-autoshow-not-giving-up-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>日元在 155 水平挣扎，市场对干预持谨慎态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/markets-wary-intervention-yen-struggles-155-level-2024-04-25/</link><description>周四，随着日本央行 (BOJ) 开始为期两天的利率制定会议，日元兑美元汇率被固定在 155 美元兑 155 美元的弱势区间，这让交易员担心东京方面是否会在政策审议仍在进行时进行干预。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 00:43:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/markets-wary-intervention-yen-struggles-155-level-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>布林肯会见上海高级官员，开启艰难的中国之行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-meet-businesses-shanghai-he-kicks-off-tough-china-trip-2024-04-25/</link><description>随着华盛顿和北京之间的关系趋于稳定，美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周四在上海会见了中国最高官员，希望在此次访问中解决一系列可能危及新修复的关系的问题。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 00:26:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-meet-businesses-shanghai-he-kicks-off-tough-china-trip-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪寻求重新定义电动汽车一代的奢华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-seeks-redefine-luxury-ev-generation-2024-04-24/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪将于周四在北京车展上展示其高端品牌的首款轿车，以向德国梅赛德斯-奔驰等公司发起挑战，后者三年前因销售缓慢而退出该品牌的开发。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 22:04:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-seeks-redefine-luxury-ev-generation-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：日本外汇未出现，Meta 暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-04-24/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 21:47:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国学生因威胁民主活动人士而在美国被判入狱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-student-gets-us-prison-term-threatening-pro-democracy-activist-2024-04-24/</link><description>周三，一名中国音乐学生在美国监狱被判处九个月监禁，罪名是骚扰一名在波士顿伯克利音乐学院张贴支持中国民主传单的活动人士，并威胁要向中国执法部门举报她的活动。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 18:44:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-student-gets-us-prison-term-threatening-pro-democracy-activist-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>拜登连任竞选不会停止使用 TikTok</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/bidens-re-election-campaign-wont-stop-using-tiktok-2024-04-24/</link><description>周三，一位竞选官员表示，乔·拜登的连任竞选活动计划继续使用 TikTok，此前不久，美国总统签署了一项法案，如果该应用程序的中国所有者未能剥离该应用程序，该法案将禁止该应用程序。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 17:23:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/bidens-re-election-campaign-wont-stop-using-tiktok-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>受中国市场推动，意大利 Moncler 第一季度销售额增长 16%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sales-italys-moncler-up-16-first-quarter-boosted-by-china-2024-04-24/</link><description>意大利时尚集团 Moncler 周三公布，按固定汇率计算，第一季度销售额增长 16%，这得益于中国强劲的需求，中国已成为一些奢侈品牌的痛处。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 16:00:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sales-italys-moncler-up-16-first-quarter-boosted-by-china-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国缓慢复苏给奢侈品行业前景蒙上阴影</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/luxury-sector-outlook-clouded-by-chinas-slow-recovery-2024-04-24/</link><description>欧洲大型奢侈品牌的最新销售数据并不能让人相信中国对高端时尚的需求正在复苏，这给该行业的前景蒙上了一层阴影。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 15:54:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/luxury-sector-outlook-clouded-by-chinas-slow-recovery-2024-04-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>